Description

clang-analyzer-osx.cocoa.MissingSuperCall
Warn about Objective-C methods that lack a necessary call to super.
The
clang-analyzer-osx.cocoa.MissingSuperCall
check is an alias, please see
Clang Static Analyzer Available Checkers
for more information.
